The autumn -  Stained glass painted on CD

body:
Finally updated an old character and actually made a reference sheet for him.

His name is Nicholas van Hyperchan, but prefers to be called Crimson. He’s of a shape shifting species that I made up years ago, but haven’t thought of a name for. This is his true form and there are a few forms of his he prefers over others out of what he has obtained during his lifetime.
